name: Bitty Sacha
description: They're so cute when they're little!  Perfectly sized for the little girl in your life...or a mini purse for you!  The "Bitty" is just big enough to hold a cell phone, sunglasses, lip gloss, a small wallet, and keys. Or perhaps tuck in a small sketch/notepad and some crayons, a snack, and a toy to keep your princess occupied! Like their larger counterparts, these purses are made with waterproof, vinyl laminated fabrics. Any fabric in the current Boodlebags collection is available.

name: Rockster Bag
description: Want a laptop bag or diaper bag with plenty of style and durability? Look no further than The Rockster! This messenger-style bag has the same features as the Miranda II, Xander, and Radster bags:  detachable back pack straps,  water-resistant exterior, and a snap-out, machine washable lining, plus plenty of pockets.  And like the others, it is more than just a diaper bag!  The exterior fabric is dark gray Cordura nylon with orange and red glitter vinyl flames applique. Light silver/gray waterproof nylon lining.  With its rugged good looks and versatile design, the Rockster bag is a great book bag, laptop or commuter bag.  Please note that while many products are in stock ready to ship, all products are hand-made and may not be in stock at the time of order.  We ship as quickly as possible, but please allow 4-6 weeks for delivery.

name: Sacha Purse
description: Sacha is a shapely little bag, and so chic! Lined with poly-cotton fabric in colors to match the exterior. Wipe-clean, waterproof exterior makes this a practical choice for tempermental weather (especially here in the Pacific NW!). Integrated cell phone and pen pockets help to keep you organized. Adjustable shoulder strap allows you to wear it cross-body or over the shoulder. Available in all Boodlebags laminated fabrics (don't see what you want? ask me!).

name: iSacha Purse
description:
Carry your iPad in style! Based on my popular "Sacha" purse with its clean, simple lines, this larger version was designed specifically to carry an iPad (or other tablet) safely in its own padded sleeve. Large open compartment has plenty of room for your other essentials, plus two pockets keep your smart phone (or pens, MP3 player, etc.) stowed close to hand and out of the clutter. Waterproof, wipe-clean exterior keeps your precious cargo dry. Adjustable shoulder strap lets you carry it high, low, or cross-body. Don't have an iPad? Me neither! How about a small notebook or sketch pad? Paperback? 

Know what else fits in this bag?  A Baby Boodle Diaper Changing Kit!  Perfect for on-the-go moms who don't want or need a big bag, but still have kiddos in diapers - and still plenty of room for essentials, snacks, and gadgets!  If you carry more than a teeny purse will hold, but hate to haul a large bag, this is a great solution!  Available in all Boodlebags laminated fabrics (don't see what you want? ask me!)

name: Radster Bag
description: The Radster joins the Xander Bag in my new line of diaper bags designed with dads in mind! Made of durable, waterproof cordura nylon, this bag is one tough customer! Dark gray with black trim, the bag has green (or orange) glitter vinyl eyes, and a toothy grimace - perfect for parents with an edgy, fun fashion sense! The Radster has all the same great features as the Miranda II, including the snap-out washable lining and backpack straps. Also a great laptop bag for computers 15" and smaller.  Please note that while many products are in stock ready to ship, all products are hand-made and may not be in stock at the time of order. We ship as quickly as possible, but please allow 4-6 weeks for delivery.  ***Please email me after placing your order to specify GREEN or ORANGE eyes!  Otherwise, I'll choose for you.***

name: Miranda II
description: The next generation of the popular Miranda bag!  Redesigned from the inside out, the Miranda II is available in many beautiful fabrics with coordinating linings and trim.  The durable, phthalate-free laminated canvas fabrics offer wipe-clean convenience and protection against leaks, spills, and our Northwest weather.  Inside, the bag lining snaps out for easy laundering!  Other improved features include an adjustable, padded shoulder strap, and adjustable backpack straps which can be removed and used as stroller straps.  Super-cute and super-practical...this is one great bag!  Please note that while many products are in stock ready to ship, all products are hand-made and may not be in stock at the time of order.
